com.poesys.db.dto

Class HasPrimaryKey<T extends IDbDto>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.poesys.db.dto.HasPrimaryKey<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of IDbDto to validate
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IValidate, java.io.Serializable

    public class HasPrimaryKey<T extends IDbDto>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IValidate
    Implements a generic validator for checking that a Data Transfer Object (DTO) has a primary key. Use this validator with any DTO.
    Author:
    Robert J. Muller
